'''Krongbing Interstellar Fashions''' was a company dealing in the manufacture of clothing in the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]].

Krongbing Interstellar Fashions came under pressure at one point in its history, and struggled to maintain profits. The company entered into a merger with [[Ayelixe Fabrico/Legends|Ayelixe Fabrico]], forming [[Ayelixe/Krongbing Textiles/Legends|Ayelixe/Krongbing Textiles]]. The former Krongbing Interstellar Fashions viewed this merger as a positive move, and Ayelixe/Krongbing Textiles later became one of the first Signatory Sponsors of the [[Corporate Sector Authority/Legends|Corporate Sector Authority]].

